substep.action:
Assemble all findings into a structured report. Format per the
severity ladder:

```md
## Self-Review Finding Report

**Reviewed**: {{ISO 8601 datetime}}
**Primary tag**: {{primary_tag}}
**Total findings**: {{N}} ({{C}} Critical, {{H}} High, {{M}} Medium, {{L}} Low)

### Critical ({{N}})
{{findings or "_(none)_"}}

### High ({{N}})
{{findings or "_(none)_"}}

### Medium ({{N}})
{{findings or "_(none)_"}}

### Low ({{N}})
{{findings or "_(none)_"}}

### Self-Review Verdict
{{BLOCK / CONDITIONAL / PASS}}
```

Store as {{self_review_report}}.

substep.output:
Self-review complete:
- Total findings: {{count}}
- Verdict (preliminary): {{BLOCK / CONDITIONAL / PASS}}
- Critical: {{count}} / High: {{count}} / Medium: {{count}} / Low: {{count}}

Proceeding to reviewer subagent dispatch (conditional on primary tag).
